{"word":"G2947 - κυλιόω - kylióō - koo-lee-o'-o - Wallow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κυλιόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kylióō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">koo-lee-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Wallow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புரள்"},{"paragraph":"to roll"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G2949 - κῦμα - kŷma - koo'-mah/2949\">G2949</a> (through the idea of <i>circularity</i>; compare <a href=\"#/G2945 - κύκλῳ - kýklōi - koo'-klo/2945\">G2945</a> and <a href=\"#/G1507 - εἱλίσσω - heilíssō - hi-lis'-so/1507\">G1507</a>); to <i>roll</i> about: - wallow.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}